name: Agrovoc
description: A controlled vocabulary covering all areas of interest of the Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO) of the United Nations, including food, nutrition, agriculture, fisheries, forestry, environment etc.

name: UN Sustainable Development Goals (SDG)
description: A value from the top-level list of UN sustainable development goals (SDGs) (e.g. ‘1’)

name: UN Sustainable Development Goals (SDG) Targets
description: A value from the second-level list of UN sustainable development goals (SDGs) (e.g. ‘1.1’)

name: Team Europe Initiatives
description: A value from the list of Team Europe Initiatives.  Team Europe consists of the European Commission, the EU Member States — including their implementing agencies and public development banks — as well as the European Investment Bank (EIB) and the European Bank for Reconstruction and Development (EBRD).
